<span id="freeTextContainer5719896361295778420">This book is amazing. This will take you through many trials and tribulations that Mr. Ufert had to live through and what he learned from each thing that passed through his life. It will open your eyes to many controversial topics not to have you changing your views but understand how adverse things can cause you to pause and look at life or situations differently and how to grow from them. Very well written, explained, and was wonderful to read. </span>

